ActCanada National Parks Act
PrecisOrder Amending the NATIONAL HISTORIC PARKS ORDER by changing the title by which this Order is known, by identifying the provisions of the Canada National Parks Act which continue to apply to national historic sites and by replacing all uses of the term national historic park with new terminology referring to them as a National Historic Site of Canada.
